---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';

const phases = [
  { num: "01", title: "Foundations at the keys", items: "Posture, hand position, and finding your way around the keyboard. First melodies come quickly - piano gives beginners early wins - while rhythm, counting, and the musical alphabet get built underneath." },
  { num: "02", title: "Reading and understanding", items: "Both clefs, note values, and playing hands together. This is also where the why starts: what a scale actually is, how chords are built from it, and why the same patterns keep appearing in every piece you learn." },
  { num: "03", title: "Chords, harmony, and real music", items: "Chord progressions, accompaniment patterns, and music the student actually wants to play - classical repertoire, modern songs, or both. Ear training threads through it all, so reading and listening develop together." },
  { num: "04", title: "Making it yours", items: "Playing expressively, learning songs by ear, improvising over progressions, and for some students, writing their own music. The keys stop being a map to follow and become a place to think." },
];
---
<Base
  path="/piano-lessons"
  title="Piano Lessons in McKinney, TX | Anthem Music"
  description="Piano lessons in downtown McKinney for all ages and levels. Classically trained instructors who teach the why behind the music - reading, technique, theory, and ear training. Book a consultation.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow" style="justify-content:center;">Piano · Keyboard</span>
      <h1 class="center">Piano lessons in McKinney</h1>
      <p class="lead mx-auto center">A classical foundation with modern application - reading, technique, and the understanding that turns notes on a page into music you own.</p>
      <div class="center" style="margin-top:1.8rem;"><a href="/schedule" class="btn btn-primary">Book a Consultation</a></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <h2>The best foundation in music</h2>
      <p>Piano is where music makes the most sense. The whole system is laid out in front of you - every note visible, every chord and scale a shape you can see. That's why the fundamentals a piano student builds - reading, rhythm, harmony, ear training - transfer to every other instrument they'll ever touch.</p>
      <p>Our piano instructors are classically trained with years of performance and teaching experience, and they teach with the patience that keeps students coming back. We work with first-time young beginners, adults returning to the keys after decades, and advancing students preparing for something bigger.</p>

      <div class="feature-grid">
        <div class="feature"><h3>Classically Trained</h3><p>Real technique and reading skills from instructors with performance backgrounds.</p></div>
        <div class="feature"><h3>The Why Included</h3><p>Theory and ear training woven into lessons - not bolted on as homework.</p></div>
        <div class="feature"><h3>Music You'll Love</h3><p>Classical, modern, worship, film scores - repertoire built around each student.</p></div>
      </div>

      <h2>How playing develops</h2>
      <p>Every student's pace is their own - age, practice, and prior experience all matter - but the arc is consistent:</p>

      <div class="milestone-list">
        {phases.map((p) => (
          <div class="milestone">
            <span class="m-period">{p.num}</span>
            <div>
              <h3>{p.title}</h3>
              <p>{p.items}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <h2>What a first lesson looks like</h2>
      <p>Every new student starts with a consultation - a one-on-one assessment where we understand your experience, goals, and how you learn. From there we match you with the right instructor and build a clear plan. No pressure, just a path forward.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-band">
    <div class="container cta-inner">
      <div><h2>Start playing piano</h2><p>Book a consultation and we'll match you with the right instructor and a plan to fit your goals.</p></div>
      <a href="/schedule" class="btn btn-primary">Book a Consultation</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .page-hero { background: var(--cream-soft); padding: clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem) 0; }
  .page-hero h1 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .narrow { max-width: 760px; }
  .narrow h2 { margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem; }
  .narrow h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  .narrow p { color: var(--gray); margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }
  .milestone-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
  .milestone { display: flex; gap: 1.4rem; background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.4rem 1.6rem; }
  .m-period { font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--orange); white-space: nowrap; }
  .milestone h3 { color: var(--navy); font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .milestone p { color: var(--gray); font-size: 0.95rem; margin: 0; }
  .feature-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 1.5rem; margin: 2.5rem 0; }
  .feature { background: var(--cream-soft); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.6rem; }
  .feature h3 { color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.15rem; }
  .feature p { color: var(--gray); font-size: 0.95rem; margin: 0; }
  .cta-band { background: var(--orange); padding: clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem) 0; }
  .cta-inner { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 2rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .cta-band h2 { color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .cta-band p { color: var(--white); opacity: 0.92; max-width: 46ch; }
  .cta-band .btn-primary { background: var(--white); color: var(--orange-dark); }
  .cta-band .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--navy); color: var(--cream); }
  @media (max-width: 700px) { .feature-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .milestone { flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; } }
</style>
